todos
=============

 * iftag
   * django has quiet extensive SmartIfParser to do that
   * dojo solution looks simpler
 * loadtag should
    {% load packageFoo.filters %}
    {% load filterBar from packageFoo.filters %}
 * autoescape
   * default: reinhardt escapes everything coming from filters/tags
   * unless: isSafe=true on the function
   * see django doc
   * also {% autoescape off %} tag

